title: PAS invited print and broadcast media to cover the opening of a new Hardees branch where CG Conroy spoke about U.S. investment in Pakistan and American firms' contribution in generating jobs. The CG also gave an interview to Urdu weekly.Family magazine where she and her parents talked about life in the U.S. and similarities between family relationships in Pakistan and the U.S
